name: THE TICKLE - Issue #25
description:
Art zine focused on Hic et Nunc artists and writers.

Issue #25 features artists Kath O'Donnell (@AliaK), Rodrigo Koshino (@koshino) and Dist Collective (@distcollective) with poetry and flash fiction by Anna Dempsey (@HeyItsAnnaDemps).

Created by artist Wily Guys (@guyswily) with help from Theo Horsmeier (@THorsmeier) and Joanne Rush (@JonicolaRush)
